Returns]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Pikachu winking and giving a thumbs up in Detective Pikachu Returns]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tech companies are selling your privacy back to you]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>安全可以赚钱。每天，公司都会兜售他们最新的隐私和安全功能，无论是在广告牌、互联网广告还是您最喜欢的节目中的广告上。就像苹果的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/19/03/14/privacy-thats-iphone-ad-campaign-launches-highlights-apples-stance-on-user-protection"><ins>“隐私”。这就是“iPhone”</ins></a>活动、 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.imore.com/new-duckduckgo-privacy-ad-shows-how-it-makes-sure-internet-trackers-are-duckduckgone"><ins>像 DuckDuckGo 这样利用隐私来使自己与众不同的浏览器</ins></a>，或者我可能因为工作而在社交媒体上投放的有针对性的 Google 网络安全广告。这有利于消费者的隐私意识，但增加了新的术语和购买决策的复杂性。</p><p>以隐私为中心的广告的复兴与数据法的流行有很大关系。这并不是说广告隐私是新事物，它可以追溯到这些公司本身，但监管使合规性成为一个卖点。 《<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/gdpr/"><ins>通用数据保护条例》</ins></a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://search.engadget.com/search;_ylt=AwrFQBTtwspkwswMVTx8BWVH;_ylc=X1MDMTE5NzgwMjg3NgRfcgMyBGZyA2VuZ2FkZ2V0BGdwcmlkA1l5WUtLVFF1UzJhckliaXF4emswQkEEbl9yc2x0AzAEbl9zdWdnAzQEb3JpZ2luA3NlYXJjaC5lbmdhZGdldC5jb20EcG9zAzAEcHFzdHIDBHBxc3RybAMwBHFzdHJsAzQEcXVlcnkDY2NwYQR0X3N0bXADMTY5MTAwOTc4Ng--?p=ccpa&amp;fr2=sb-top&amp;fr=engadget"><ins>《加州消费者隐私法》</ins></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/state-of-privacy-laws-in-us/"><ins>其他各种当地法律的</ins></a>出现迫使公司优先考虑数据隐私，同时消费者也关注数据隐私。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Beacon Digital Marketing 首席执行官兼创始人惠特尼·帕克·米切尔 (Whitney Parker Mitchell) 告诉 Engadget，在幕后，当法规落实到位时，合规人员就会被雇佣来做出购买决策，隐私和安全也会得到新的重视。从那里，公司根据目标买家决定是否做广告隐私和安全合规性广告。</p><p>米切尔说：“你在哪里强调这一点以及在营销材料中提供多少信息实际上取决于它对主要买家的重要性。”就像感觉非常个性化的手机可能会优先考虑安全性一样，但您可能更看重便利性，而不是机器人真空吸尘器等产品中的任何东西。</p><p>尽管如此，隐私和安全是密集和复杂的，使得这些概念不太适合简洁的口号。通常，当营销人员试图将其简化为吸引人的东西时，重要的细微差别就会丢失，或者流行语会模糊现实。 “广告活动可能会让问题看起来比实际情况更简单或过于简单化，”未来隐私论坛的广告技术和平台技术专家兼高级政策分析师 Aaron Massey 表示。</p><p>梅西告诉 Engadget，这类似于柠檬市场——二手车，而不是水果。做出营销声明很容易，但买家很难确认其真实性，因为他们没有专门的技能来验证它。</p><p>因此，为了配合广告活动，我们的设备上也出现了更多对消费者友好的隐私意识。国际隐私专业人士协会 (International Association of Privacy Professionals) 常务董事 Cobun Zweifel-Keegan 表示：“企业正在认识到，隐私政策不足以真正帮助消费者了解数据的真实情况。”这包括隐私检查等工作，引导您在登录时弹出窗口来更新设置。</p><p>这对于隐私和安全来说是积极的。更多的监管和消费者教育最终推动了这些广告的发展。不过，在相信它们的表面价值之前，您应该注意一些事情。虽然不可能每条广告都 <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/DPL_rewind/status/1677533215110701056"><ins>全面而详细地介绍</ins></a>该主题，但诸如“我们是最安全的”之类的主观主张应该会引起怀疑。 Zweifel-Keegan 告诉 Engadget：“最好寻找公司可以明确支持的说法，以及首席隐私官或安全官等高级人员的支持。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tech-companies-data-privacy-ads-marketing-183049670.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tech-companies-data-privacy-ads-marketing-183049670.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f69644b7-b95d-45ce-aa4f-b4e35b819abb</guid><dc:creator>凯蒂·马龙</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 08 Aug 2023 18:30:49 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691519396</ingested><modified> 2023-08-08T18:30:03+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Katie Malone]]></category><media:content height="1883" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ad2a8750-3616-11ee-bbef-f2a796c8f381" width="3000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1883" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ad2a8750-3616-11ee-bbef-f2a796c8f381" width="3000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Katie Malone]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An Apple "Privacy. That's iPhone." ad on the side of a building in Washington, DC featuring a person holding an iPhone in front of their face.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[An Apple "Privacy. That's iPhone." ad]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Netflix just released a game controller app for the iPhone]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Netflix 继续进军视频游戏，该公司刚刚推出了一款<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2FwcHMuYXBwbGUuY29tL3VzL2FwcC9uZXRmbGl4LWdhbWUtY29udHJvbGxlci9pZDY0NDc1ODI1ODEiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImRmNjgzNzUxLTlhY2YtNDkxYS04ODY4LTFhNTM1Mzg2OGI5NCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAfXQdjsfcmKv6Nez6HbpV6o1biefxEWUOsNd0NCA2rL2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fnetflix-game-controller%2Fid6447582581" class="rapid-with-clickid"><ins>针对 iOS 设备的专用控制器应用程序。</ins></a>该应用程序简称为“Netflix Game Controller”，一旦将设备与电视配对，您就可以将手机或平板电脑用作游戏手柄。这将允许您在电视上玩通过 Netflix 服务提供的游戏，同时通过移动设备进行控制。</p><p>尽管该应用程序已经可供下载，但进一步的消息仍然很少。例如，我们不知道它将支持哪些游戏或有关配对过程的任何细节。我们也不知道 Android 应用程序是否以及何时会跟进。该应用程序的描述只是戏弄游戏手柄功能“即将在 Netflix 上推出”。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>考虑到该公司作为独立游戏发行商的不断增长，这并不令人意外。 Netflix Games 在过去两年中发布或托管了近 70 款游戏，其中一些可以通过常规 Netflix 流媒体应用程序访问，其他则可以在移动设备和游戏机上使用。这些游戏也不是一次性的游戏，就像<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/oxenfree-ii-lost-signals-will-hit-switch-netflix-steam-and-playstation-on-july-12th-173603739.html"><em><ins>《Oxenfree II: Lost Signals》</ins></em></a>这样的游戏在发布时就广受好评。 <em>Oxenfree</em>开发商 Night School 现已成为<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/why-the-oxenfree-ii-team-became-netflixs-first-game-studio-130035607.html"><ins>Netflix 的第一个内部工作室。</ins></a></p><p>未来几个月将登陆 Netflix 平台的其他影片包括<em>《Storytellers》、《Paper Trail》</em>和《<em>纪念碑谷》</em>系列等独立热门影片。还有一款<em>《刺客信条》</em>游戏正在开发中，以及手机游戏<em>《乐高：遗产英雄未装箱》</em>的移植版。可以肯定的是，您应该能够使用最近推出的控制器应用程序来玩其中一些游戏。 Engadget 联系了 Netflix，询问兼容性以及 Android 版本的可能性。公司发言人表示，目前不发表评论。</p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/netflix-just-released-a-game-controller-app-for-the-iphone-181609420.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/netflix-just-released-a-game-controller-app-for-the-iphone-181609420.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> df683751-9acf-491a-8868-1a5353868b94</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 08 Aug 2023 18:16:09 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691518570</ingested><modified> 2023-08-08T18:16:16+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mobile Apps]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="540" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/a6de21e0-3616-11ee-9eb4-3940fd05c9c0" width="960"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="540" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/a6de21e0-3616-11ee-9eb4-3940fd05c9c0" width="960"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Netflix]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Netflix Games logo.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Netflix Games]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Netflix adds text-based 'Heart of Stone' game to its Discord bot]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>自去年以来， <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/netflix/">Netflix</a>运行了一个<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/discord/">Discord</a>机器人，可以帮助人们根据所在位置的可用内容找到可以一起观看的节目和电影。该公司目前正在通过基于文本的游戏扩展<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://discordbotlist.com/bots/netflix">“嘿，Netflix”机器人的</a>功能。</p><p>这是 Netflix 首次在 Discord 上推出此类游戏。正如你可能想象的那样，它与你很快就能在 Netflix 上播放的一部名为<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XuDwndGaCFo"><em>《石之心》的</em></a>动作片联系在一起<em>&nbsp;</em>由盖尔·加朵和杰米·多南主演。该片将于本周五登陆 Netflix。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>在<em>《石之心：几率迷宫》</em>中，您将扮演双重间谍的角色（类似于加朵在电影中的角色）。 Netflix 表示，你需要在“行动驱动的情况”下快速做出决定。根据Netflix提前分享的一些细节，你似乎需要在一些预设选项之间进行选择，就像它过去发布的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-03-12-netflix-interactive-shows-bandersnatch.html">互动电视节目和电影</a>一样。</p><p>有趣的是，Netflix 表示，每次玩<em>《石之心：奇数迷宫》</em>都会有所不同。 Discord 机器人从一组情况中随机选择场景。此外，您还可以单独玩游戏或邀请朋友加入多人游戏。游戏还包括供您沿途拾取的收藏品。最后，虽然世界各地的 Discord 用户都可以体验这款游戏，但值得注意的是，它只有英文版本。</p><p>过去几年，Netflix 一直大力进军游戏领域。上个月， <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/why-the-oxenfree-ii-team-became-netflixs-first-game-studio-130035607.html">它发布了<em>Oxenfree II</em></a> ，这是其内部工作室的第一款游戏。该公司还刚刚<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-just-released-a-game-controller-app-for-the-iphone-181609420.html">推出了一款适用于 iPhone 和 iPad 的游戏控制器应用程序</a>。因此，您很快就可以在兼容的电视以及手机和平板电脑上玩其游戏（通常包含在 Netflix 订阅中）。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/netflix-adds-text-based-heart-of-stone-game-to-its-discord-bot-174216893.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/netflix-adds-text-based-heart-of-stone-game-to-its-discord-bot-174216893.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0ec57466-4587-49a6-b92a-800b5dcec94e</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 08 Aug 2023 17:42:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691523733</ingested><modified> 2023-08-08T19:42:17+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Movies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="730" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/756a1580-360f-11ee-a37f-36fe9bcb825a" width="1296"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="730" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/756a1580-360f-11ee-a37f-36fe9bcb825a" width="1296"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Netflix]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Gal Gadot in Netflix movie Heart of Stone. A woman lies on snowy ground  with her arms outstretched and he hands out of the frame. She is looking at something outside of the frame.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Gal Gadot in Netflix movie Heart of Stone.]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple is reportedly testing M3 chips for new Macs arriving this fall]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-08-07/apple-tests-2024-m3-max-macbook-pro-chip-with-16-cpu-cores-40-gpu-cores">据</a><em>彭博社</em>报道，苹果正在测​​试 M3 芯片的变体，第一批运行新 Apple Silicon 的 Mac 可能<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apples-first-m3-macs-could-arrive-in-october-163204526.html">最早于 10 月上市</a>。据报道，与<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-updates-its-mac-book-pros-with-m-2-pro-and-max-chips-143848558.html">1 月份才上市的</a>M2 Max 相比，高端笔记本电脑芯片 M3 Max 将拥有四个更多的高性能 CPU 核心和至少两个额外的图形核心。</p><p>据报道，该公司正在测试新的 iMac、13 英寸 MacBook Pro、13 英寸和 15 英寸 MacBook Air 和 Mac mini，所有产品都运行 M3 芯片，预计在未来 12 个月内测试。配备 M3 Pro 和 M3 Max 芯片的更新版 14 英寸和 16 英寸 MacBook Pro 型号可能要到 2024 年才会上市。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>该公司可能会采取积极的 Mac 发布计划，因为其台式机和笔记本电脑产品线在<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/report-apple-sold-a-record-number-of-mac-books-last-quarter-091233817.html">大流行时代的繁荣</a>后难以重新获得销售基础。尽管它在 6 月份推出了<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-macbook-air-15-inch-review-a-bigger-screen-makes-a-surprising-difference-130033172.html">15 英寸 MacBook Air</a> ，并在 1 月份推出了新款<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-macbook-pro-14-inch-review-2023-m2-pro-max-140048268.html">MacBook Pro</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/mac-mini-review-m2-pro-2023-140052205.html">Mac mini</a> ，但今年秋天我们可能会看到更多新的 Mac 硬件。 （该公司在上周的<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-services-are-making-more-cash-than-ever-but-revenue-shrank-for-the-third-quarter-in-a-row-205545482.html">财报电话会议</a>上暗示，新的 Mac 电脑要到 9 月底结束的第四财季之后才会上市。） 据<em>彭博社</em>报道，苹果确实计划在 10 月份推出产品。</p><p>据报道，基础 M3 芯片将使用与 M2 相同的配置：8 个处理器核心和最多 10 个图形核心。然而，M3 Pro 将从 12 个 CPU 核心和 18 个图形核心开始，测试日志表明 M3 Max 将包括 16 个 CPU 核心和 40 个图形核心。当然，苹果可能正在测试核心数量选项的多种变体，但我们尚不知道哪些版本将提供给消费者。</p><p>长期以来一直有传言称，M3 芯片将转向<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/intel-and-apple-expected-to-debut-3-nm-processors-next-year-100632556.html">台积电即将推出的 3 纳米工艺，与 M2 中使用的 5 纳米工艺相比，预期性能和效率将得到</a>改善。人们还普遍预计苹果将在<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-15-pro-set-to-feature-a-thinner-bezel-titanium-frame-and-usb-c-charging-094118389.html">即将推出的 iPhone 15 系列</a>中使用 3nm 工艺的 A17 芯片。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-reportedly-testing-m3-chips-for-new-macs-arriving-this-fall-173457588.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-reportedly-testing-m3-chips-for-new-macs-arriving-this-fall-173457588.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 69d7aaa5-91d5-4cfa-8e47-c14f342672cb</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 08 Aug 2023 17:34:57 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691516098</ingested><modified> 2023-08-08T17:35:05+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Computing]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="3233" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/460b8200-3610-11ee-a7d7-eda8ad2abcfd" width="4618"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3233" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/460b8200-3610-11ee-a7d7-eda8ad2abcfd" width="4618"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - Apple CEO Tim Cook stands in front of a display of new Apple MacBook Air computers with M2 processors, Monday, June 6, 2022, following the keynote presentation of Apple's World Wide Developer Conference on the campus of Apple's headquarters in Cupertino, Calif. Apple's foray into live sports took a big step forward Tuesday, June 14, 2022. Apple and Major League Soccer have announced a 10-year partnership on a streaming service that will allow fans to watch every game without local blackouts or restrictions. The service will be available exclusively through the Apple TV app beginning next year. (AP Photo/Noah Berger, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[MLS Apple]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best cameras for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>现在是购买数码相机的奇妙而美好的时机。由于智能手机已经蚕食了休闲摄影市场，制造商正专注于打造专为特定用途而设计的技术奇迹。无反光镜相机在自动对焦、视频等方面不断改进。运动摄像机提供清晰、流畅的视频，紧凑型相机面向游客和视频博主，单反相机的价格是我们见过的最优惠的。不过，数码相机的类型多种多样，您可能需要一些指导才能找到合适的相机，这就是我们的用武之地。无论您是正在寻找合适的视频博客相机的创作者、有抱负的野生动物摄影师还是摄影师，作为运动爱好者，我们将帮助您找到适合您的预算和需求的完美相机系统。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-cameras-151524327.html#mirrorlesscamerasunder2000">2,000 美元以下的最佳无反光镜相机</a></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-cameras-151524327.html#mirrorlesscamerasover2000">2,000 美元以上的最佳无反光镜相机</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-cameras-151524327.html#bestactioncamera">最佳运动相机</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-cameras-151524327.html#bestcompactcamera">最好的紧凑型相机</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-cameras-151524327.html#bestdslrcamera">最佳数码单反相机</a></p><h2>选择相机之前要考虑什么</h2><p>选择相机而不是智能手机的原因有很多。无反光镜相机中更大的图像传感器可以让更多的光线进入，并且您有多种镜头选择，从广角到长焦再到变焦镜头，具有更优越的光学性能。智能手机只有一个光圈值，而相机有很多光圈值，这可以让您更好地控制曝光。您还可以获得自然的而非人工智能生成的散景、更快的拍摄速度、物理快门、更专业的视频效果等等。</p><p>然而，随着质量的提高，还有许多额外的因素需要考虑。首先是传感器尺寸。一般来说，传感器尺寸越大，相机越好（通常也更昂贵）。</p><p>全画幅适用于索尼新款 ZV-E1、佳能 EOS R6 II 和松下 S5 II 等型号。它的尺寸相当于 35 毫米胶片 (36 x 24 毫米)，在图像质量、低光能力和景深方面提供最佳性能。它也是最昂贵和最挑剔的。虽然散景在 f/1.4 时看起来令人难以置信，但景深非常薄，以至于拍摄对象的鼻子可能在焦点上，但不是他们的眼睛。这也会给视频拍摄带来困难。 </p><div id="17e6cba906c140a2ad6d0203360809e0"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ESI72hUjqNA?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p>下一个尺寸类别是 APS-C（大多数型号约为 23.5 x 15.6 毫米，佳能约为 22.2 x 14.8 毫米），在富士胶片的 X 系列产品线、佳能的 R10 和 R50 以及尼康 Z50 上提供。无论是相机机身还是镜头，它都比全画幅便宜，但仍然具有大部分优点，如良好的散景、适合低光拍摄的高 ISO 和相对较高的分辨率。它的传感器尺寸与电影摄影机相同，非常适合拍摄视频，并且比全画幅相机更容易保持对焦。</p><p>松下和奥林巴斯共享的微型三分之四 (17.3 x 13mm) 格式是传感器尺寸的下一步缩小。与 APS-C 和全画幅相比，它提供的散景和聚光能力较少，但允许使用更小、更轻的相机和镜头。对于视频，您仍然可以使用优质定焦镜头获得相当紧密的景深，但焦点更容易控制。</p><p>另一种常见的传感器尺寸是 1 型（1 英寸），实际上小于 1 英寸，尺寸为 12.7 x 9.5 毫米。主要用于索尼 ZV-1 视频博客相机等紧凑型型号。最后，GoPro Hero 11 和 DJI Osmo 3 等运动相机的传感器甚至更小（尺寸分别为 1/1.9 和 1/1.7）。</p><p>对于业余和专业摄影师来说，另一个关键因素是出色的自动对焦 (AF) 速度和准确性。大多数现代无反光镜相机都具有混合相位检测自动对焦系统，可实现快速对焦和快速连拍。大多数还具有人工智能智能功能，例如针对人和动物的眼睛检测自动对焦。然而，有些模型只是比其他模型更快一点、反应性更强一些。</p><p>电子取景器（EVF）和后显示屏也是关键。最好的型号拥有最清晰、最明亮的电子取景器，让您在拍摄前最好地判断拍摄结果。对于街头摄影之类的事情，最好有尽可能明亮和锐利的后显示屏。您可能还想要一个可以翻转而不仅仅是倾斜的屏幕。</p><p>数码单反相机和无反光镜相机可以让您更换镜头，但您只能使用紧凑型相机的内置镜头。虽然这对于便携性来说非常有利，但单镜头意味着您将牺牲一些东西。例如，Fujifilm 的 X100V 具有快速但固定的 35mm 等效 f/2.0 镜头，并且没有变焦。索尼的 RX100 V 具有 24-70 毫米变焦，但在长焦端 (f/2.8) 速度较慢，而且清晰度不如定焦镜头。</p><p>当谈到视频时，还有其他因素需要考虑。您的相机是否对视频录制进行“像素合并”或读取整个传感器？更好的相机往往会做后者。另一个关键因素是传感器速度，因为较慢的传感器往往有更多的滚动快门，可能会产生使视频倾斜的“果冻”效果。</p><p>另外，电池寿命如何？您喜欢它的操控性和感觉吗？在相机变热或停止之前，您可以拍摄视频多长时间？支持 10 位 HDR 视频吗？有麦克风和/或耳机插孔吗？ （如果您进行大量采访，最好两者都进行。） 视频自动对焦怎么样？所有这些因素都会影响您的决策 - 所以现在让我们来看看最好的模型。</p><h2>最好的相机</h2><h3>最好的无反光镜相机</h3><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-mirrorless-cameras-133026494.html">无反光镜</a>无疑是当今最大的相机类别，因此如果您想要具有最先进功能的最佳摄影相机，那么无反光镜是最好的选择。佳能和尼康最近都宣布他们将停止开发新的数码单反相机，仅仅是因为该类别的大部分优势都消失了，正如我在<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:YouTube;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=89f68c82-f255-44fa-8db9-03fec996b93a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=YouTube&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4OWY2OGM4Mi1mMjU1LTQ0ZmEtOGRiOS0wM2ZlYzk5NmI5M2EiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj1ueVBLQkJlSHk2ayZ0PTFzIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIzNjg0YzFhZS03MTQ1LTRkYzItOWQ4OC0zMGRmZGZlZGFkYTIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAaSW4adeV86kjVHSaZugxT9y3OFpmPGeYld4L6Wu_zQd&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnyPKBBeHy6k%26t%3D1s">最近的视频</a>中详细介绍的那样。无反光镜相机的最大卖点是能够根据您想要进行的拍摄类型更换镜头。</p><p>主要特征是传感器尺寸、分辨率、自动对焦、拍摄速度和视频规格。如果您主要专注于体育摄影或户外摄影，您可能需要快速的拍摄速度和准确的自动对焦。肖像和风景拍摄者可能会青睐大传感器和高分辨率，以最大限度地提高图像质量。内容创作者会希望寻找翻转式显示屏、高端视频规格和良好的体内稳定性等功能。当然，价格也是一个主要因素。</p><h2> 2,000 美元以下的无反光镜相机</h2><h3>2000 美元以下最佳无反光镜相机：佳能 EOS R50</h3><p><core-commerce id="0fcc4f5a6ca94f0cbad34ddc2cb015e8" data-type="product-list"></p><p>我最喜欢的预算相机是佳能全新的 24.2 兆像素<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:B&amp;H Photo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=95276f3c-7b79-4c1e-803f-981cd9f7a968&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=B%26H+Photo&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQGNPOAPTjbMo8fI_NOy6A_tkuqZ8i7BBW96k7vQwVHQ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1748810-REG%2Fcanon_eos_r50_mirrorless_camera.html">R50</a> ，它是最好的摄影相机之一，内容创作者一定会喜欢它。它可以在电子快门模式下以高达 15 fps 的速度连拍，并以高达 30p 的速度提供 4K 10 位，具有超级采样和无裁剪功能。它有一个完全铰接的显示屏，与这个价格范围内的其他相机不同，它有一个电子取景器。它使用佳能的双像素自动对焦和主体识别模式，甚至还有弹出式闪光灯。唯一的缺点是缺乏像相机本身一样价格实惠的优质镜头，并且缺乏机身稳定性。</p><ul><li><p>自动对焦：双像素 CMOS AF II，651 点</p></li><li><p>最大快门速度：15 fps</p></li><li><p>无线网络：有</p></li><li><p>蓝牙：有</p></li></ul><h3>亚军：佳能EOS R8</h3><p><core-commerce id="a787745eaeb240478f510108eeabb707" data-type="product-list"></p><p>以前全画幅相机的起价通常为 2,000 美元以上，但佳能全新的<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbAei0t33-uU6JuLpkMzHI1ExD4-TvaQaFb7I4kE3eBP&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCanon-Full-Frame-Mirrorless-Lightweight-Smartphone%2Fdp%2FB0BTTTH5G6%3Fth%3D1">EOS R8</a>售价仅为 1,500 美元。它提供佳能出色的双像素自动对焦和人工智能主题识别功能，并能以高达 40 fps 的速度进行连拍。它在视频方面同样强大，支持高达 60 fps 的过采样 10 位 4K。 R8 还提供翻转式显示屏，非常适合视频博主。主要缺点是缺乏体内稳定性。</p><h3>另一个不错的选择：松下 Lumix S5 II</h3><p><core-commerce id="0c4d97c5afa54dbc809d30fa6768ca4c" data-type="product-list"></p><p>内容创作者应该仔细看看<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:B&amp;H Photo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=95276f3c-7b79-4c1e-803f-981cd9f7a968&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=B%26H+Photo&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXS79eG_Lwa-CBFBcKPyylApACGfhOxX2X-0DGWyUbLc&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1742428-REG%2Fpanasonic_dc_s5m2body_lumix_s5_ii_mirrorless.html">松下的全画幅 S5 II</a> 。这是该公司第一款采用混合相位检测自动对焦的<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/panasonic-s5-ii-review-the-full-frame-vlogging-camera-youve-been-waiting-for-150028638.html">相机</a>，旨在使焦点“抖动”和其他问题成为过去。您可以从整个传感器宽度下采样拍摄清晰的 4K 30p 视频，或从 APS-C 裁剪尺寸拍摄 4K 60p 视频，全部采用 10 位颜色。它甚至提供 5.9K 30p 捕捉，以及 RAW 5.9K 外部输出到 Atomos 录音机。您还可以获得用于视频博客的翻转屏幕和业界最佳的更新五轴体内稳定功能。得益于双增益 24 兆像素传感器，照片质量也很好。主要缺点是突发速度较慢。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/panasonic-s5-ii-review-the-full-frame-vlogging-camera-youve-been-waiting-for-150028638.html">阅读我们对松下 Lumix S5 II 的完整评论</a></p><h2>无反光镜相机超过 2,000 美元</h2><h3>2000 美元以上最佳无反光镜相机：索尼 ZV-E1</h3><p><core-commerce id="808f7f977eb7493786e9b9b06fa3d499" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Tb255LUZ1bGwtRnJhbWUtSW50ZXJjaGFuZ2VhYmxlLU1pcnJvcmxlc3MtQ2FtZXJhL2RwL0IwQlpXTldDWjk_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby11dS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMzY4NGMxYWUtNzE0NS00ZGMyLTlkODgtMzBkZmRmZWRhZGEyIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAZTU1q8RvqilGwdTOj2mn_UqxBAeCCaJBZBAoKrWfvvS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Full-Frame-Interchangeable-Mirrorless-Camera%2Fdp%2FB0BZWNWCZ9%3Fth%3D1">索尼 ZV-E1</a>配备与 A7S III 相同的背照式 (BSI) 12 兆像素传感器，提供<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sonys-12-megapixel-full-frame-zv-e1-is-a-low-light-vlogging-beast-140009036.html">出色的低光性能</a>、高达 120p 的 4K 以及自动取景等一系列新的 AI 功能，使其成为摄影和摄像的最佳相机。它还配备了针对视频博主的更新的体内图像稳定（IBIS）系统，可以平滑脚步等震动。 2,200 美元的价格标签对视频博主来说很有吸引力，因为它以相当低的价格提供了 3,500 美元的 A7S III 的功能。</p><ul><li><p>自动对焦：759点</p></li><li><p>最大快门速度：10 fps</p></li><li><p>无线网络：无</p></li><li><p>蓝牙：有</p></li></ul><h3>亚军：富士X-H2S</h3><p><core-commerce id="fd89ed7a9b454a13b0853f1265bb675b" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您可以使用较小的 APS-C 传感器，请查看<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9GdWppZmlsbS1YLUgyUy1NaXJyb3JsZXNzLUNhbWVyYS1Cb2R5L2RwL0IwQjJGNVZITE0_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tdXUtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjM2ODRjMWFlLTcxNDUtNGRjMi05ZDg4LTMwZGZkZmVkYWRhMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdI4J0wZt--Z9Pt5jI6_MzXeazc_YkxSPdkpYFzWPFwJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFujifilm-X-H2S-Mirrorless-Camera-Body%2Fdp%2FB0B2F5VHLM">Fujifilm X-H2S</a> 。它具有令人难以置信的快速堆叠式背照式 26.1 兆像素传感器，可实现 40 fps 的快速连拍速度，并以最小的滚动快门拍摄 4K 120p 视频。它可以在内部捕获 ProRes 10 位视频，具有 7 档体内稳定功能和一流的 EVF。是的，对于 APS-C 相机来说它很昂贵，但另一方面，它是整体上最便宜的堆叠传感器相机。另一个缺点是自动对焦不太达到佳能和索尼的水平。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/fujifilm-x-h2s-mirrorless-camera-review-123049866.html">阅读我们对 Fujifilm X-H2S 的完整评论</a></p><h3>另一个不错的选择：索尼A7R V</h3><p><core-commerce id="6323f269e5014a62a630b86bfe5bb056" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如需终极高分辨率相机，请查看<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Tb255LUZ1bGwtRnJhbWUtTWlycm9ybGVzcy1JbnRlcmNoYW5nZWFibGUtQ2FtZXJhL2RwL0IwQktMUUZGU0Y_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby11dS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMzY4NGMxYWUtNzE0NS00ZGMyLTlkODgtMzBkZmRmZWRhZGEyIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAVwf83dHGTo3WONrR1FZq3XI4_9vEx31tmFXhxYpZTX8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Full-Frame-Mirrorless-Interchangeable-Camera%2Fdp%2FB0BKLQFFSF%3Fth%3D1">索尼 A7R V。</a> With a 61-megapixel sensor, it shoots sharp and beautiful images at a very respectable speed for such a high-resolution model (10 fps). It has an equally fast and reliable autofocus system, the sharpest viewfinder on the market and in-body stabilization that&#39;s much improved over the A7R IV. Video has even improved, with 8K and 10-bit options now on tap, albeit with significant rolling shutter. If you don&#39;t need the video features, however, Sony&#39;s A7R IVa does mostly the same job, photo-wise, and costs a few hundred dollars less.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-a7r-v-review-awesome-images-improved-video-unbeatable-autofocus-150058082.html">Read our full review of the Sony A7R V</a></p><h2> Best action camera</h2><p> The most important features to look for in an action cam are image quality, stabilization and battery life. GoPro has easily been beating all rivals over the last few years in all those areas, but DJI made some strides last year with the Osmo Action 3. At the same time, GoPro&#39;s latest models are more expensive than rivals.</p><h3> Best action camera: GoPro Hero 11 Black</h3><p><core-commerce id="6c030b4e0a724884b6ea95512376ff9d" data-type="product-list"></p><p> GoPro didn&#39;t change the design on its latest model, but it has a larger sensor that enables a couple of cool features – Horizon Lock stabilization and Full Frame mode that makes it easier to shoot for, say, TikTok and YouTube at the same time. It also offers a new wider, though slightly distorted Hyperview field of view.</p><p> Otherwise, the <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:GoPro;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=06fa1f29-e83c-49e4-81a8-9732450da8a9&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GoPro&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQxGXJQH_IppkyCdZjAB32vthp2txOLVTmKYXpTnYRrS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fgopro.com%2Fen%2Fus%2Fshop%2Fcameras%2Fhero11-black%2FCHDHX-111-master.html">Hero 11 Black</a> offers better video quality than ever (up to 5.3K 60p), Hypersmooth stabilization that&#39;s still the best in the business (by far), battery life that&#39;s improved by 40 percent over the last model, and more. It&#39;s easily the best action camera on the market, but you pay for that: it&#39;s $400 with a one year subscription ($500 without it), compared to $329 for the DJI Osmo Action 3 and $300 for the Insta360 RS 4K bundle. If you&#39;re serious about filming extreme sports, though, it&#39;s worth it.</p><ul><li><p> WiFi: Yes</p></li><li><p> Bluetooth: Yes</p></li></ul><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gopro-hero-11-review-125905853.html">Read our full review of the GoPro Hero 11</a></p><h3> Runner up: DJI Osmo Action 3</h3><p><core-commerce id="42d2cf364079470392365a559708f0a0" data-type="product-list"></p><p> After experimenting with an oddball modular design on the Action 2, design has gone back to a more classic action cam design on the <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ESkktU3VwZXItV2lkZS1Ib3Jpem9uU3RlYWR5LVdhdGVycHJvb2YtTG9uZy1MYXN0aW5nL2RwL0IwQjdYMkxYUTY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tdXUtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjM2ODRjMWFlLTcxNDUtNGRjMi05ZDg4LTMwZGZkZmVkYWRhMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAfCLlzGupjmaFNj3gORx9vZ6hl-uM421pYSWosTHwFIx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDJI-Super-Wide-HorizonSteady-Waterproof-Long-Lasting%2Fdp%2FB0B7X2LXQ6">Osmo Action 3</a> . It also comes with a slick new magnetic quick-release mount that lets you connect the camera directly to a GoPro-style mount with or without the case. Video quality and stabilization are quite good, but fall short of the Hero 11 Black (the Action 3 tops out at 4K 120p resolution compared to 5.3K 60p on the GoPro). While it&#39;s not quite as good as the Hero 11, it&#39;s considerably cheaper.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/dji-osmo-action-3-far-more-battery-life-fast-charging-and-a-spiffy-new-mount-120035233.html">Read our full review of the DJI Osmo Action 3</a></p><h2> Best compact camera</h2><p> This category has fewer cameras than it did even a few years ago and many models are older, as manufacturers focus instead on mirrorless models. However, I&#39;m still a big believer in compact cameras. This type of camera is a big step up from smartphones quality-wise, and a lot of people will take a compact traveling or to events when they&#39;d never bother with the hassle of a DSLR or mirrorless camera.</p><p> Compacts largely have type 1-inch sensors, but a few offer larger options, particularly Fujifilm&#39;s XF-100V. Another popular model, Sony&#39;s XV-1, is primarily aimed at content creators looking to step up. In any case, desirable qualities include image quality, a fast lens, relatively long zoom, flip-out display, good battery life, a high quality EVF, decent video and good pocketability.</p><h3> Best compact camera: Fujifilm X100V</h3><p><core-commerce id="92f4461aa31f4807b9b9d196a69e2c94" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Adorama;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=0eee6f60-6f21-4ba6-b70e-cc15b39bf860&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Adorama&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIwZWVlNmY2MC02ZjIxLTRiYTYtYjcwZS1jYzE1YjM5YmY4NjAiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYWRvcmFtYS5jb20vaWZqeDEwMHZzLmh0bWwiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjM2ODRjMWFlLTcxNDUtNGRjMi05ZDg4LTMwZGZkZmVkYWRhMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAbZrABxIdUjxo2_QKkiEyqsbIKzN_vVi5pbbI4KJYg3n&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adorama.com%2Fifjx100vs.html">X100V</a> is the latest in Fujifilm&#39;s famous fixed-lens X100 camera series. Like other models in the lineup, it has an APS-C sensor and a 23mm f/2.0 lens, equivalent to 35mm on a full-frame sensor. You also get the same hybrid optical/electronic viewfinder, mechanical dials, film simulations and good looks as before. But the X100V is the most significant advancement in the series&#39; history. It has Fujifilm&#39;s latest 26.1-megapixel X-Trans 4 CMOS sensor compared to 24.2-megapixels on the last model and a new, sharper lens to handle that extra resolution.</p><p> A new tilting rear display makes &quot;shooting from the hip&quot; street photography much easier, as does the fast 11 fps/20 fps shooting speeds in mechanical/silent shutter modes. You also get a better hybrid phase- and contrast-detect autofocus (AF) system with more AF points along with face and eye detection. Finally, it now has the same 4K video-shooting features as the X-T30. It doesn&#39;t come cheap, but the X100V is the ultimate camera if you&#39;re into street photography – assuming you can <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.dpreview.com/forums/thread/4695587">find one</a> .</p><ul><li><p> Max shutter speed: 20 fps</p></li><li><p> WiFi: Yes</p></li><li><p> Bluetooth: Yes</p></li></ul><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-03-24-fujifilm-x100v-compact-camera-review.html">Read our full review of the Fujifilm X100V</a></p><h3> Runner up: Sony ZV-1</h3><p><core-commerce id="29d538fa485747f8b79db21757ef7d58" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaWp66eHqX1HYzlVjbEpsDrBC9YQpv-LJNpm4HH_FbKt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Content-Creators-Vlogging-Microphone%2Fdp%2FB08965JV8D%3Fth%3D1">ZV-1</a> is Sony&#39;s first RX100-series camera designed specifically for vlogging. It does that job well thanks to a lightweight body, built-in high-quality microphone, flip-out display, best-in-class autofocus and excellent image quality. The 24-70mm lens is sharp, but it needs to be wider because of the 25 percent crop when using electronic stabilization. It also lacks a true touch display and a headphone port. That nitpicking aside, if you&#39;re looking to step up from a smartphone or just want something simple, it does the job nearly perfectly.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-zv-1-vlogging-camera-review-162822651.html">Read our full review of the Sony ZV-1</a></p><h3> Another good option: Panasonic ZS-200</h3><p><core-commerce id="833d101b29c24d6a94cd943ab7b81b5f" data-type="product-list"></p><p> For a value compact camera, the best option is Panasonic&#39;s 20-megapixel <a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUezUfxPy2h-trf4jyr95QCSAAv0yL6EO77foAFnUdtj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPANASONIC-Stabilization-Megapixel-Sensor-DC-ZS200S%2Fdp%2FB079QNXFCC%3Fth%3D1">ZS-200</a> . It offers a lot of features for the price, like a 1-inch, 20.1 megapixel sensor, 5-axis stabilization, 4K, 30 fps video and more. Its main claim to fame, though, is the 24-360x lens that offers incredible reach for travel and more. Though it dates back to 2018, it&#39;s actually one of the more recent compact models.</p><h2> Best DSLR camera</h2><p> With mirrorless cameras taking over the interchangeable lens market, DSLRs still give you the ability to change lenses at relatively cheap prices. The defining feature is the reflex mirror that lets you look directly through the lens at your subject with no electronics in between. Most also have very fast autofocus thanks to a dedicated phase-detect sensor, and very fast battery life. However, many lack features you&#39;d expect on modern mirrorless cameras like subject tracking, eye-detection and more.</p><h3> Best DSLR camera: Nikon D850</h3><p><core-commerce id="13aeb905f00642c09cb5661564f8ebeb" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Nikon&#39;s full-frame (FX) <a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASKBTK1v7wIk9EBRLRFgcu_J1t23aEedlVLba83Si1V0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNikon-D850-FX-Format-Digital-Camera%2Fdp%2FB07524LHMT%3Fth%3D1">D850</a> is the best deal on a high-end camera and arguably the best camera for photography. With a 45.7-megapixel sensor and max 102,400 ISO, it gives you the best quality for the money, whether mirrorless or DSLR. It can also shoot fast, at up to 7fps, which is very good for such a high-res camera. In addition, the battery life (1840 shots on a charge) puts any mirrorless option to shame, and there&#39;s a massive number of FX Nikkor lens options to choose from. Nikon has upped its video game as well with the D850 by introducing 4K internal recording. If you&#39;d still rather have a live optical rather than an electronic view, the D850 is the best option available.</p><ul><li><p> Autofocus: 153 points</p></li><li><p> Max shutter speed: 7 fps</p></li><li><p> WiFi: Yes</p></li><li><p> Bluetooth: Yes</p></li></ul><h3> Runner up: Canon EOS Rebel SL3</h3><p><core-commerce id="e341516cb4374770afb8e580d860eec7" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Another one of the best cameras for photography is Canon&#39;s 24-megapixel APS-C <a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASwImYIK8e5-fOTXlj2rbEEcYAUK69jT9uXLtHPplmJv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCanon-Rebel-18-55mm-Lens-White%2Fdp%2FB07QHPT781%3Fth%3D1">EOS Rebel SL3</a> , which has a great blend of features, build quality and value. It offers features like a vari-angle touchscreen, 4K video (albeit with a crop) and Dual Pixel autofocus technology in live mode. You get shooting speeds of up to 5 fps, 1600 shots on a charge and an ISO range up to 51,200 (expanded). It also offers guided screen options for beginners. Best of all, it offers excellent picture quality for the price thanks to Canon&#39;s skin-friendly color science.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-cameras-151524327.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-cameras-151524327.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3684c1ae-7145-4dc2-9d88-30dfdfedada2</guid><dc:creator> Steve Dent</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 08 Aug 2023 16:55:13 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691513714</ingested><modified> 2023-08-08T16:55:24+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Cameras & Photography]]></category><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1238" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-02/cb39b890-b2f6-11ed-afff-4d399c6315d8" width="2200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><me